title: [LFT] Bot lane player (Support/ADC) from EU, just starting in OCE
body:
Hey everyone,

Title says all, I am looking for a team in OCE, moved a few months ago to Sydney for Europe and I would like to be part of a team again :) Regular schedules are fine if you have one, can also swap at will between adc and support depending on what is needed.

Got Skype/TS/Mumble, I play LoL since beta, Plat 3 last year in EU, 27 m living in Sydney. I recycled a friend's account level 30 who left Australia, add me in game (nick: Gorzewski) if you want to duo / 5v5 any time :)

Cheers!

replies.body: Hey!, I'll add you in-game, I used to play in EUW too and we are about the same age... hopefully we can play duo at nights and soon get on a reg schedule team. I main support. Wellcome to Oz. Vertigo Rampage

Hey mate welcome to OCE


Hope you enjoy your stay! :)

Good luck on your search
I do! Thanks for the "support" mate (sorry, had to do it)
